  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>1. Tender & Pre-Contract</strong></p><ul><li><p>Tender preparation, quantity take-offs, pricing</p></li><li><p>Subcontractor & supplier sourcing</p></li><li><p>Technical clarifications with operations team</p></li><li><p>BQ / drawings / spec discrepancies & RFIs</p></li><li><p>Commercial evaluation & negotiation</p></li><li><p>Technical proposal documentation & submissions</p></li></ul><p><strong>2. Contract & Commercial Management</strong></p><ul><li><p>Earned value & projected final account reporting</p></li><li><p>Variation identification, submission & closure</p></li><li><p>Progress claims & payment certification</p></li><li><p>Prime contract & subcontract administration</p></li><li><p>Final accounts settlement</p></li><li><p>Time & cost claims support</p></li></ul><p><strong>3. Project Support & Planning</strong></p><ul><li><p>Method statements & execution plans</p></li><li><p>QA/QC, HSSE documentation</p></li><li><p>Project schedules & resource planning</p></li><li><p>Coordination with internal stakeholders</p></li></ul>",
